程序包 com.ftp.client

类 FTPClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ftp.client.FTPClient
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    StreamLogging
    public class FTPClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements StreamLogging
    FTP client for modern FTP servers, which must implement both RFC 959 and RFC 3659.

      • FTPClient

        public FTPClient​(java.lang.String addr,
                 int port)
          throws java.io.IOException
        Connect to FTP server. To retrieve response, see ControlSocket.getStatusCode() and ControlSocket.getMessage().
        参数:
        addr - FTP server address
        port - FTP server port
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - exception thrown by Socket connection

    • 方法详细资料

      • login

        public boolean login​(java.lang.String user,
                     java.lang.String pass)
              throws java.io.IOException
        Login for ftp client. For anonymous login, try 
        
 ftp.login("anonymous", "");
        参数:
        user - username for ftp account
        pass - password for ftp account
        返回:
        true if access granted.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - thrown if controlSocket went wrong.

        public java.lang.String[] rawList​(java.lang.String dir)
                           throws java.io.IOException
        Raw response of LIST command. Calling this method directly is strongly discouraged, though some FTP server only support this command, rather than MLSD.
        参数:
        dir - remote directory to list.
        返回:
        raw response.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - .

      • list

        public FTPPath[] list()
               throws java.io.IOException
        Current directory listing with LIST and MLSD.
        返回:
        Array of FTPPath, or null if the server side happen to not support MLSD.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - .
        另请参阅:
        FTPPath, list(String dir)

      • list

        public FTPPath[] list​(java.lang.String dir)
               throws java.io.IOException
        Directory listing with LIST and MLSD. Note that some ancient FTP server may not support MLSD, so good luck.
        参数:
        dir - Remote directory.
        返回:
        Array of FTPPath, or null if the server side happen to not support MLSD.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - .
        另请参阅:
        FTPPath

      • chdir

        public boolean chdir​(java.lang.String dir)
              throws java.io.IOException
        Change current directory. Syntax like "..", relative path and absolute path are supported as well.
        参数:
        dir - Remote directory.
        返回:
        false if directory not found else true
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - .
